{"tid":2189413,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蘋果日報 兩岸 20200905 星期六","createTime":"2020-09-05T01:11:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-05T01:16:13.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"93281b1148edfe189fcfe216a542a11bf835fa04","tid":2189413,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T01:11:08.000Z","msg":"蘋果日報 兩岸 20200905 星期六<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/daily/china/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fdaily%2Fchina%2F&d=RlZLtXxvTyjhSejQ4AJs4yC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=9f4ce7a3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fdaily%2Fchina%2F&h=88c76599\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/daily/china/</a><br />\n<br />\n7小時前<br />\n「艱辛探索」觸怒紅二代 補鑊改回「領導者錯誤」 課本表述文革 回歸鄧《決議》<br />\n<br />\n習近平<br />\n7小時前<br />\n針對美區分「中共」與「中國人」 習提「五個絕不答應」<br />\n<br />\n7小時前<br />\n四港企違反伊朗禁令 遭美國制裁<br />\n<br />\n7小時前<br />\n楊潔篪訪歐 疫苗外交拉攏西班牙<br />\n<br />\n7小時前<br />\n中印外長下周俄會晤 衝突後首次<br />\n<br />\n■加利董事長林明進（右二）堅稱沒賣黑心口罩，昨被帶返工廠調查。台灣蘋果新聞網<br />\n7小時前<br />\n混售陸口罩台廠 指政府逼增產  當局展示合約反駁 蔡英文促查<br />\n<br />\n■維特齊（左三）、酈英傑（右三）、吳釗燮（右二）等一同出席「重組供應鏈」論壇。台灣蘋果新聞網<br />\n7小時前<br />\n拒屈服華恐嚇 捷議長稱經貿須對等<br />\n<br />\n■網傳解放軍戰機在桂林墜毀。<br />\n7小時前<br />\n中共戰機墜廣西 台否認擊落<br />\n<br />\n7小時前<br />\n捍衞母語 內蒙女公僕跳樓亡<br />\n<br />\n7小時前<br />\n遭華拘捕澳籍作家拒認間諜<br />\n<br />\n============"},{"pid":"f8ffb3d1c01f01eb4eaa5f8576bb065cad9a185e","tid":2189413,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T01:16:13.000Z","msg":"習近平：黨國體制，黨=國，我=黨<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.chainnews.com/material/images/b098fb2bf8319f6c18f6f1bf538c44d4.jpg-article\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.chainnews.com%2Fmaterial%2Fimages%2Fb098fb2bf8319f6c18f6f1bf538c44d4.jpg-article&h=1bf507e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wCGoXOm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwCGoXOm.jpg&h=bd8ad3b9&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}